So Endometriosis converts at ~37% end-to-end while everyone else is between 61-70%. Looking at the step-level chart above, the gap really opens up at Intake → Match — which strongly suggests it's a provider supply issue (not enough endo specialists on the platform) rather than patients losing interest.
## 3. Cohort retention

Once a patient sees a provider, do they come back? Cohort here = the month a patient joined.
